[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "よし……アーシャさんの話によると、\nキースさんは今、宝石パイプを持ってるはず",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "ふふん、つまりそのパイプがある場所に\n「亜空の道」を繋げれば、どこに居てもイタズラ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "じゃなくて、パイプの替えを届けられるってわけね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "そう！　世界に１つしかないパイプなら、\n場所を特定するのも簡単だし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "あんた、なかなか頭回るじゃない。\n面白くなってきたわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "アーシャさんからもらったパイプを基に、キースさんが\n居る場所に「亜空の道」を繋げる道具を調合だー！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "リディー",
		"romanized_name": "Lydie",
		"model_path_hash": "7496495454778535986",
		"text": "あれ？　二人ともなにしてるの？　\nなんだかすごく楽しそうだね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "650002066085119948",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "うんうん、なんだかワクワクする雰囲気だよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "リディー、ロロナさん！　\nちょうどいいところに来たね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "今から「亜空の道」でキースさんにパイプの替えを\n届けようと思ってるんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "リディー",
		"romanized_name": "Lydie",
		"model_path_hash": "7496495454778535986",
		"text": "「亜空の道」？　よく分からないけど、　\nそんなことして大丈夫なの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "650002066085119948",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "大丈夫よ、あたしたちがついてるんだから。\n失敗しても、面白い思い出になるって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "それに、今回はちゃんと「届け物」があるんだし、\nイタズラじゃないよーっと！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "リディー",
		"romanized_name": "Lydie",
		"model_path_hash": "7496495454778535986",
		"text": "……本当に？　なんだか不安だなぁ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "650002066085119948",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "でも、せっかくだし協力しようかな。\n「亜空の道」、わたしも気になるし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "さっすがロロナさん！　\nもちろんリディーもやるんだからね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "リディー",
		"romanized_name": "Lydie",
		"model_path_hash": "7496495454778535986",
		"text": "う、うん……分かった。\nロロナさんもやるなら、最後まで付き合うよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "650002066085119948",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "じゃあ、みんなで調合開始ね！　\nあたしは素材の選別をやるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "リディーは触媒の調整お願い！　\nロロナさんはこの宝石パイプの解析をしてもらえる？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "うん、任せて！　これくらいならきっと大丈夫",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（しめしめ……これだけの面子が揃えば、\n　「亜空の道」もなんとかなるよね！）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "あんた、顔がニヤけてるわよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "だって、絶対面白いことになるもん！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "リディー",
		"romanized_name": "Lydie",
		"model_path_hash": "7496495454778535986",
		"text": "……やっぱりイタズラに使うんじゃないかなあ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "650002066085119948",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]